以守護家園名義打鳩我地，<br />\n再加上輿論帶風向，比人打又係我地，<br />\n理虧亦都係我地。<br />\n<br />\n上次何妖單野，無論係邊個做，<br />\n理虧都係我地呢邊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住一樣野，令你愈high嘅野通常都會愈毒。"},{"pid":"7105b61e5416538e4e7d0cc17f586d2d06066e5f","tid":1358783,"uid":279913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"如果將自己變埋做黑道，仲點有理據去反3黑？ 如果燒錯咗1個半個無辜者，咁同白衣人有何分別？ 別讓憤怒蓋過理智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3da4deaeefa5f26a359f3e7a6253cdb04abbcd5","tid":1358783,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"冷靜咗落黎 發覺有無可能可以拉埋正義既鄉民入埋黎"},{"pid":"53271c447079361705007b9e8608d8119d8526a1","tid":1358783,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d33e6cba650d3550a0494c4c1b9674e933ac191","tid":1358783,"uid":121557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:46:35.000Z","msg":"727 和理優 不入村 不開波 對家郁手會還拖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3952836ba6ce53746c4ecb8413ae454222e52827","tid":1358783,"uid":40849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"hi錯咗負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b794cc8dc836b81c6f70e8faceb48fd879ba9137","tid":1358783,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3da4deaeefa5f26a359f3e7a6253cdb04abbcd5","tid":1358783,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"冷靜咗落黎 發覺有無可能可以拉埋正義既鄉民入埋黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"就算拉唔到原居民 都可以拉到班其他非原居民嘅元朗人"},{"pid":"9f3d591cad6a267cc5685acba4da994a627899d4","tid":1358783,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3952836ba6ce53746c4ecb8413ae454222e52827","tid":1358783,"uid":40849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"hi錯咗負評<img src=\"/assets/faces